TITLE: Example .env File Configuration for Telegraf
DESCRIPTION: Sample .env file format for storing environment variables used by Telegraf bots, including port, webhook domain, and bot token. This file should be added to .gitignore to prevent credential leakage.
SOURCE: https://github.com/feathers-studio/telegraf-docs/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
# .env
PORT=3000
WEBHOOK_DOMAIN=bot.example.com
BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABC-DEF1234ghIkl-zyx57W2v1u123ew11
```

