TITLE: Complex filtering in Telegraf for combined conditions
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to filter updates based on multiple conditions simultaneously, such as forwarded text messages or photos that are part of a media group. This allows for precise handling of specific update scenarios.
SOURCE: https://github.com/feathers-studio/telegraf-docs/blob/master/guide/002-listen-and-respond.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: TS
CODE:
```
// Listen for text messages that were forwarded
bot.on(message("forward_from", "text"), ctx => {
	// These properties are accessible:
	ctx.message.text;
	ctx.message.forward_from.first_name;
});

// Listen for photos messages that are part of an album (media group)
bot.on(message("photo", "media_group_id"), ctx => {
	// These properties are accessible:
	ctx.message.photo;
	ctx.message.media_group_id;
});
```

