TITLE: Sending initData for Validation in Web App
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code demonstrates how to send the initData from a Mini App to a server for validation using a fetch request.
SOURCE: https://github.com/feathers-studio/telegraf-docs/blob/master/examples/mini-apps/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
window.addEventListener("ready", async function () {
	const data = await fetch(
		"/validate-init",
		{ method: "POST", body: app.initData },
	).then(res => res.json());
});
```

